# KSAO Workforce Development Project Overview

This project analyzes Knowledge, Skills, Abilities, and Other characteristics (KSAOs) for substance use disorder counselors using Gemini AI. The repository follows a structured approach to extract KSAOs from textbook materials using OCR and advanced text analysis.

## Main Components

1. **Text Extraction Pipeline**: Uses Gemini OCR to extract text from TIFF scans of textbook pages
2. **KSAO Analysis Pipeline**: Analyzes extracted text to identify and categorize KSAOs
3. **Visualization Pipeline**: Creates network visualizations of identified KSAOs

## Directory Structure

- `src/`: Source code with modular structure
- `data/`: Input data (scans and extracted text)
- `output/`: Generated outputs (analysis results, visualizations)
- `docs/`: Documentation and presentations

## Key Files

- `src/main.py`: Central entry point for all functionality
- `gemini_ocr.py`: OCR processing using Gemini AI
- `src/ksao/analyze_full_textbook.py`: Core KSAO extraction logic
- `src/ksao/visualize_ksao_network.py`: Network visualization generation

When developing, ensure your code follows the existing patterns and integrates with the modular structure.